<h1>Add a Podcast</h1>

<h4>Found or created?</h4>
<p>Is this your podcast, or did you find it?  If this is your podcast, the email listed in the
feed should match the email that you used when you signed up for LimeCast.  You can change your
email on the account settings page.</p>

<h4>Feed URL</h4>
<p>The feed url is sometimes referred to the RSS feed or the XML feed.</p>

<% form_remote_tag(:url => feed_info_podcasts_path, :update => 'form_placeholder') do -%>
  <p>
    <%= label_tag "feed" -%><br />
    <%= text_field_tag :feed -%>
    <%= submit_tag "Get Feed" -%>
  </p>
<% end -%>

<div id="form_placeholder"></div>


<%= link_to 'Back', podcasts_path %>
